#%RAML 1.0 DocumentationItem
title: Overview
content: |
  The System Control Plane API provides a canonical contract for analysis job lifecycle operations.

  It is the Mule-native replacement for the retired Go control-plane HTTP surface and is intended
  for Process API orchestration and MCP/agent tool delegation.

  This specification inherits shared governance assets from:
  - mule-utility-template-spec (template baseline)
  - mule-utility-common-fragment (shared security/traits/resource types)
